com.interpss.core.acsc.fault.result

Interface IFaultResult_dep

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IBranchScCurrent, IBusScVoltage, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface IFaultResult_dep
extends IBusScVoltage, IBranchScCurrent
    For calculating and storing fault result information. After a fault analysis, the FaultPoint Voltage, Fault Point SC Amp and Fault Point Equiv Z are stored in the object. In addition, bus SC voltages of all buses are stored. They are used, together with the AcscNetwork object to calculate branch currents 1) Fault impedance (zFault) 2) Fault point equivalent impedance (zEqFault) Source Volt |--- zNetFault ---o--- zEqFault ---o zFault = zNetFault + zEqFault
